N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 5 ยง 120.6 - Cost sharing

State Regulations

Any expenditure for an export diagnostic assessment or export
market development plan shall be based upon an application approved by the
commissioner, and in no case shall the level of contribution by the eligible
applicant toward such assistance be less than 50 percent of the total costs of
such assistance. Notes
